Securing APIs with Authentication (C#)
Question:
Fill in the blank to secure an API in C# by adding JWT Bearer authentication using the correct authority and audience.

csharp

services.AddAuthentication(JwtBearerDefaults.AuthenticationScheme)
        .AddJwtBearer(options =>
        {
            options.Authority = "https://__________";  // Fill in the blank
            options.Audience = "api1";
        });
